metadata.title: 4PC Value Pack Lot Clear Acrylic Staple Septum Nose Ring Retainers (Metal-Free)
features: Hide a septum piercing with this retainer
These are sold in packs of 4. You choose the gauge and you'll receive four of that particular size.
description: Septum retainers are pieces of jewelry designed to make your piercing less visible (or not at all). Acrylic is a popular substitute to use with your piercings if you have a metal sensitivity.
